      "short": "",
      "value": "<p>This warm tea infused with magical spices functions like a serum (Starfinder Core Rulebook 225) and fortifies the mind and spirit when imbibed. Cafes near the Radiant Cathedral are often filled daily with Sarenite clerics enjoying this beverage while talking about the confluence of science and religion. Drinking this brew grants you a +2 insight bonus to Diplomacy, Mysticism, and Physical Science checks for 1 hour, and during that time you can attempt checks to recall knowledge with Mysticism and Physical Science untrained.</p>",
